OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly morning low cloud quickly
OL,6,Fburning back to the coast, turning
OL,7,Fsunny by the afternoon before low
OL,8,Fcloud returns in a freshening
OL,9,Fnortheasterly wind. Temperatures very
OL,10,Fwarm inland but cooler along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLow cloud over the North Sea
OL,13,Fwill spread quickly inland covering
OL,14,Fthe whole region by the morning,
OL,15,Fdriven by a strong breeze along the
OL,16,Fcoast. Temperatures remain mild
OL,17,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
